fronted cryptotechcoder
   bind *:80
   mode http
   default_backend app

backend app
   balance roundrobin
   server 439003-web-01 54.204.203.255:80 check
   server 439003-web-02 54.152.35.0:80 check" >> /etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg

